    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_4__BRIEFING_2_GALAMAR:
        "Only in the heavily guarded fortresses of Thorin will the Crystal be safe. We must deliver it there.",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_4__BRIEFING_3_SOLDIER: "Your Majesty, our scouts report enemy troops nearby!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_4__BRIEFING_4_SOLDIER:
        "They are destroying our buildings to cripple our supply of gold! They must be stopped!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_4__BRIEFING_5_GALAMAR: "Captain, we must save the Crystal, prepare the troops for battle!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_4__BRIEFING_6_SOLDIER: "Your Majesty, We have stopped the attack.",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_4__BRIEFING_7_GALAMAR: "Well done, Captain! Prepare the troops to march to Thorin!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_5__BRIEFING_1_SOLDIER:
        "Your Highness, I do not like the look of this forest, we must be careful!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_5__BRIEFING_2_GALAMAR: "Very well, Captain. Let us follow this path and stay on our guard.",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_5__BRIEFING_3_SOLDIER: "Ambush! Protect the Crystal at all cost!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_6__BRIEFING_1_VALADORN:
        "The enemy is planning to attack King Galamar before he reaches Thorin! We must defeat them!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_6__BRIEFING_2_VALADORN:
        "Let us hurry North to meet Galamar. The enemy knows of his plans and he may need help!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_7__BRIEFING_1_DEMON_LORD: "Run, pitiful human, before it is too late!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_7__BRIEFING_2_SOLDIER: "The enemy force looks formidable, I recommend retreat.",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_7__BRIEFING_3_GALAMAR: "We have no choice but to attack!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_7__BRIEFING_4_VALADORN: "Galamar! We came as fast as we could! Let us fight side by side!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_1_GALAMAR: "The Ruins of the Ancient Citadel... and Saeth! With the Crystals!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_2_SAETH:
        "At last, Galamar and Valadorn! How very brave of you to confront me! All the keys are now in place, and soon the greatest power ever created on this earth will roar and bend to my will. Your destruction will be testimony to its might and glory!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_3_VALADORN: "Your ruses can no longer fool us, Saeth!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_4_NO_IMAGE: "TARGET AQUIRED...\n\nHEAVEN'S FURY ACTIVATED!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_5_GALAMAR: "Heaven's Fury? What in the name of the Creator is that!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_6_SAETH:
        "Pathetic creatures, this is something ancient that you would not understand even if you lived a thousand years! Witness the power of Heaven's Fury!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_7_VALADORN: "Galamar! We must hurry if our troops are to stand a chance!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_8_SOLDIER:
        "Sire, we should attack these castles first before we launch an attack on the Saeth and the Ruins.",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_9_SAETH:
        "Pitiful wretches. You will not live long enough to see your precious Kingdom engulfed in shadow...",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_10_GALAMAR: "Saeth! This time your defeat is complete!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_11_SAETH:
        "In your insignificant life and narrow mind, perhaps... Nevertheless everything is now set in motion - the invisible forces that govern time are beyond your knowledge. You cannot stop me from rising again!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_12_SOLDIER:
        "Your Majesty, the Ruins are falling apart! We should leave immediately!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_13_TAMPLIER: "But the Crystals... They are still in there!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_14_VALADORN: "The only thing we can save now is ourselves!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_15_GALAMAR: "You have served me well. Now move!",
    MAP_NAME__AE2_MISSION_8__BRIEFING_16_NO_IMAGE:
        "And thank you for playing 'Ancient Empire: Strike Back' - I very much hope you enjoyed playing it as much as I enjoyed making it!",
